<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.1.1">
<l>vaṇṇa māṭaṅkaḷ cūḻtiruk kōṭṭiyūr</l>
<l>kaṇṇaṉ kēcavaṉ nampi piṟantiṉi</l>
<l>leṇṇey cuṇṇa metiretir tūviṭak</l>
<l>kaṇṇaṉ muṟṟam kalantaḷa ṟāyiṟṟē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When Lord Kṛṣṇa Keśava was born in</l>
<l>Tirukkōṭṭiyūr, surrounded by decorated mansions,</l>
<l>Sesame oil and [tumeric] powder were sprinkled, combining [with each other],</l>
<l>mixing [on the ground] of Kṛṣṇa’s court-yard such that it became mud.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
